Company Overview of Redwood Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Redwood Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals and other pooled investment vehicles. It launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. Redwood Capital Management, LLC was founded in 2000 and is based in Englewood Cliffs, New Jersey.


